title: Miss Americana & The Heartbreak Prince
description:
This isn't just your high school fight song, but it does pack a punch. What is Taylor saying in this song? And what was the defining moment that made her take a stand? And how does Harry Potter tie into all of this? SHE REALLY DOES THINK OF EVERYTHING!

Plus, Taylor really is just like the rest of us... and she's peeping!
Nick, Ana, Amy and Lacey dissect and discuss everything in Miss Americana & The Heartbreak Prince!

What did we miss? What would you like for us to discuss? Let us know!
